data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!  Indulge in opulence with this exquisite property situated on a prime waterfront lot.  This impeccably maintained, practically new, single level home seamlessly blends functionality with style, featuring a spacious open floor plan and 12-foot ceilings that create an airy ambiance.  Revel in the luxury of Mohawk 6X24 Tile Plank flooring throughout the living areas, while the bedrooms boast upgraded luxury vinyl for a touch of elegance.  The study/den, foyer and formal dining room form a captivating entry, leading to a family room with a three-door slider showcasing pond views where you can watch the wildlife all day.  The kitchen, which is open to the family room, is adorned with white Timberlake cabinetry, Mohawk backsplash, square edge Daltile quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances for all your culinary proclivities.  The primary retreat is bathed in light and offers a serene en-suite with double quartz vanities, large soaking tub and spacious shower.  Additional features include new gutters and the patio is pre-plumbed for a future outdoor kitchen.  The Watergrass community is close to everything Wesley Chapel has to offer as well as offering many amenities of it’s own.  Resort style pools, fitness area, playgrounds, tennis courts and Watergrass Elementary are all on-site, while hospitals, shopping and dining are just a few minutes away. Why wait for new construction when you can start living your dream now!
